elp of Sparkle Paddle Payment Gateway Lite Plugin.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://ps.w.org/sparkle-paddle-payment-gateway-lite/assets/banner-772x250.png?rev=2610098\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:842px;height:auto\"/></figure><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/sparkle-paddle-payment-gateway-lite/\"><strong>Download Sparkle Paddle Payment Gateway Lite Plugin</strong></a></h2><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Key Features</strong></h3><ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>You can avail automatic refund processing system with this plugin.<br></li>\n\n<li>You can change and update the gateway titles as per your requirements.<br></li>\n\n<li>This plugin provides assistance for EDD debugging.<br></li>\n\n<li>You can have a list of predefined gateway icons.</li>\n\n<li></li>\n\n<li>You can get the benefits of lifetime free updates.</li></ul><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Price Structure</strong></h3><p>The Sparkle Paddle Payment Gateway Lite Plugin is completely FREE for its users.</p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>4. HandyPlugins PaddlePress Plugin</strong></h2><p>The free version of HandyPlugins PaddlePress Plugin helps you to easily integrate Paddle with WordPress. You can accept credit cards and create Paddle accounts in a few minutes with this plugin. Also, the pro version of HandyPlugins PaddlePress Plugin is feature-rich and more powerful.</p><p>Your customers can seamlessly access their account information and data by using the member dashboard created with the Paddle API plugin. You can create unlimited membership plans and unlimited maps with the Paddle product creator.</p><p>As per your requirement, you can set up and restrict content appearance on your website to a certain level of members. It will be beneficial for you to use this plugin if your website is developed to sell domain-based license keys.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-im